28
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:22,560
Danyu,

29
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,080
you were too reckless just now.

30
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,610
If it wasn't for Brother Li, you would have...

31
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:27,740
Brother Li,

32
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,320
your hand is bleeding.

33
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:32,000
Xiaoxue!

34
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,320
The Power of Heaven!

35
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:39,850
This is a refining material comparable to Origin Blood.

36
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:42,930
Xiaoxue,

37
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,520
you suffered internal injuries.

38
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,320
Is it serious?

39
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:46,720
Miss Mu,

40
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:47,900
your injury...

41
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,320
Xiaoxue,

42
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,240
is it because of the aftershock just now?

43
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,120
It's all my fault.

44
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,450
I failed to protect you.

45
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,880
Wuzhou,

46
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,120
don't panic.

47
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,000
My injury is not serious.

48
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,160
I can still hold on.

49
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,680
Brother Li,

50
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,220
how are your injuries?

51
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:11,080
It really is the classic cliché of the second male lead falling for the female lead.

52
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,160
But,

53
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,600
Demon Lord, oh, Demon Lord.

54
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,400
You two will never be happy.

55
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,280
In this small world,

56
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,920
the female lead belongs to the male lead.

57
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:21,780
If you actually fall in love with the female lead...

58
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,520
But you...

59
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,579
Borrow it for a moment.

60
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,280
You...

61
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,280
Hey.

62
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,120
What are you doing?

63
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:49,760
Healing.

64
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,400
Let me go.

65
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,720
I'm here again.

66
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,730
Consciousness.

67
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,840
He said I have

68
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,960
the purest Source Blood in the world.

69
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,760
Likong.

70
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,420
The Likong clan

71
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,040
has naturally special blood.

72
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,200
The energy within it

73
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,740
is a supreme medicine for the Nether Demons.

74
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,560
Although it has no effect on humans,

75
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,400
it provides a multiplied boost to

76
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,200
sacrifices, seals, and talisman drawing.

77
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,079
So,

78
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,640
they used their blood as an exchange

79
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,440
to seek the protection of the Tiandao Palace.

80
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,600
Tiandao Palace?

81
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,400
If you have

82
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,880
the purest Source Blood,

83
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,660
you would definitely be heavily protected.

84
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,560
At least ten Foundation Establishment disciples of Tiandao Palace

85
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,360
would stay by your side at all times.

86
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,160
How could you grow up outside?

87
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,320
I know this.

88
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,880
It should be her mother

89
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,000
who took her out of

90
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,480
that palace you mentioned.

91
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,280
Ran away?

92
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:01,200
I don't have the extra energy to trace this history for now.

93
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,400
We can only wait for a chance in the future

94
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,660
to find out the reason.

95
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,370
Now, remember this.

96
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:08,720
Before, the demon lord used himself as a foundation to sacrifice the Daughter of the World,

97
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,250
unleashing supreme power,

98
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,840
and ultimately destroying the world directly.

99
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,920
The Daughter of the World is suitable for the heavenly sacrifice

100
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,320
because of her special soul.

101
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,040
And you,

102
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,959
possessing the purest Source Blood,

103
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,760
are even more suitable than her.

104
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:24,040
So I'm also suitable for this heavenly sacrifice.

105
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,760
What a sad reality.

106
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,000
From another perspective,

107
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,260
it's also a good thing.

108
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,040
At least,

109
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:32,290
he probably won't want to kill you in the near future.

110
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,640
That seems to make sense.

111
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,800
The world's trajectory

112
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,640
has completely shifted now.

113
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,250
I don't know how it will develop later.

114
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,020
But having changes

115
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,680
is a good thing after all.

116
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,080
It's just that

117
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,090
I can't stay awake all the time.

118
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,300
You can only rely on yourself for now.

119
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,760
You're going to sleep again?

120
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,200
Little Yiyi?

121
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,160
Goodbye.

122
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,400
I've finished chatting.

123
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,920
Why isn't he done yet?

124
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,800
Hurry up.

125
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,040
Are you done?

126
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,040
I'm about to become anemic.

127
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,760
Was I talking too loud just now?

128
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,240
Anyway,

129
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,840
he's like this now

130
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,600
because he saved us.

131
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,640
Um...

132
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,840
Thank you.

133
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,560
Thank you for saving us.

134
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,090
Aren't you afraid of me?

135
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,720
That's a different matter.

136
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,600
You saved us,

137
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,880
so you are our benefactor.

138
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,810
Thanking you is the least we can do.

139
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,800
Is that so?

140
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,010
Then remember this.

141
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,400
Your life now

142
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,000
belongs to me.

143
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:56,580
This is supposed to be a bossy CEO speech,

144
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,960
so why does it sound so cringeworthy?

145
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,520
Danyu.

146
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,460
Brother Li.

147
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,240
Where did you take Danyu?

148
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,680
Ask her.

149
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,160
Danyu,

150
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,980
your injuries are all healed?

151
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,920
Went to treat my injuries.

152
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,240
Went to treat my injuries.

153
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:26,800
You went to

154
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,730
treat injuries?

155
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,560
Danyu,

156
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,080
are you

157
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,200
really healed?

158
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,560
Yes.

159
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,250
My injuries are all healed.

160
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,640
Just a little anemic.

161
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,580
Brother Li,

162
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,680
your injuries

163
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,920
look a bit serious.

164
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,409
I can hold on for now.

165
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:52,490
Xiaoxue,

166
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,250
are you feeling better?

167
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,680
It's fine now.

168
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,080
Since

169
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,240
everyone is here,

170
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,120
let's go.

171
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,800
Wuzhou,

172
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,240
although there are no demons in this village,

173
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,320
demonic energy still lingers.

174
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:06,960
Remember

175
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,760
to notify a sect that can clear it

176
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,880
to deal with the aftermath.

177
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,600
Don't worry.

178
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,000
Later,

179
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,760
I will notify the cultivators of Tiandao Palace

180
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,560
to handle it.

181
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,450
Let's go.

182
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,200
Danyu,

183
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,800
let me sleep with you tonight.

184
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,560
I can stay up all night to take care of you.

185
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,490
No need, no need.

186
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,659
Look, my injuries are all healed.

187
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,040
Then,

188
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,880
how about

189
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,170
I give you a massage?

190
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,440
After fighting all night,

191
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,560
you must be tired.

192
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,680
No thanks.

193
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,360
I'm sleepy.

194
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,940
Let's just go to bed early.

195
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:43,800
Then how about

196
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:46,159
we go back and take a bath together to relax?

197
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,760
I'd rather not.

198
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,960
She has to serve me when we get back.

199
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:53,159
I don't have time to play house with you.

200
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,800
Let's begin.

201
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:20,840
Chunyi.

202
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,440
We only have five

203
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,700
blood talismans left.

204
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,480
How many do you plan to use

205
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,640
in this village?

206
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,410
Use them all.

207
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,400
All of them?

208
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,140
This...

209
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,280
The Likong clan is scarce now,

210
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,360
and the supply of blood talismans is decreasing every year.

211
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,159
We should use them sparingly.

212
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,679
You're right.

213
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,210
We should save them.

214
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,600
But...

215
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,680
The demonic aura in this village is too heavy.

216
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,010
If we don't use them all,

217
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,920
I'm afraid we can't settle this.

218
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,720
Alright.

219
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,320
When we get back,

220
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,520
I must apply for a subsidy from the sect.

221
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,240
But Chunyi,

222
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,280
this Likong clan is

223
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,560
too weak, isn't it?

224
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,400
Our Heavenly Dao Palace

225
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,360
raises them with the best resources,

226
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,520
and gives them priority for all the good stuff.

227
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,480
We disciples

228
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,810
don't even get our turn.

229
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,770
Yet the people of their clan

230
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,140
are actually decreasing every year.

231
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,840
Is it really that hard

232
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,320
just to provide some blood talismans?
